author: dlr
msg: In an attempt to avoid test failures resulting from invocation of
the cmdline test scripts from outside of their own directory (a
fairly common pitfall), be much more obvious about which directory
a test script must be invoked from.

msg: * subversion/tests/cmdline/README: Fix some paths missed in r17718 / r18324.

author: djh
msg: Change the VS2005 'ignore deprecation' definitions to match

author: julianfoad
msg: Tell and enable callers of the new svn_wc_revision_status() not to rely on
the size of the results structure, so that we can transparently extend the
structure in future.  This is a follow-up to r18266.
(svn_wc_revision_status_t): Note that callers shouldn't rely on its size.
(svn_wc_revision_status): Make the result pointer an output parameter.
